embed.description: In this video I tested the brand new game mode on the PBE, called "PROJECT: OVERCHARGE"! I really enjoyed playing and I think that it will be great fun to play when it comes to the live servers! Thank you for watching! Make sure to leave a like/comment if you like the video.
